1540:Generated_Source\PSoC5/ADC_DelSig_1.c **** *  configuration, the ADC is stopped and powered down. After setting
1541:Generated_Source\PSoC5/ADC_DelSig_1.c **** *  the new configuration, the ADC can be powered and conversion
1542:Generated_Source\PSoC5/ADC_DelSig_1.c **** *  can be restarted depending up on the value of second parameter
