1545:Generated_Source\PSoC5/ADC_DelSig_1.c **** *  and ADC_DelSig_1_StartConvert() to restart the conversion.
1546:Generated_Source\PSoC5/ADC_DelSig_1.c **** *
1547:Generated_Source\PSoC5/ADC_DelSig_1.c **** * Parameters:
